AlainFace
\n<Alain>I finally got out of that town, but what
the heck?!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Is she seriously that much bigger than
the town? This is even beyond Micro, isn't
it?
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Oh wow! You managed to open one of the gates!
You really ARE the partner of Ciel's Chosen One!\c[0]
\n<Celyn>\c[27]But you're still so itty-bitty... Even to a
faerie like me. I'm okay with listening to you now, but
I don't think I can even hear you.\c[0]
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Why don't you climb up higher? All the way
up here? Teehee~!\c[0]
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Ehehe~! I love watching you Itty-Bitty Ones
struggle. I must be a mountain to you, right? You
better hurry up. If I get bored, I might just
forget about you.\c[0]
AlainFace
\n<Alain>I know I saw them before, but they're
still just so huge. Their voices are more
deafening than thunder.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>She's right, too. Even if I try to
shout up at her, there's no way my voice
can even get past her skirt.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>I'll have to climb up as high
as I can - all the way up to her face.
Celyn's Challenge
Find a way to the top of Celyn's body. If you take too
long, Celyn's magic will make Alain too small.
SpriteZoom.zoom(0, 0.4);
\n<Celyn>\c[27]You're taking too long~! Hurry up, Itty
Bitty One! Or else you'll never make it up to me~
Ehehehe~!\c[0]
SpriteZoom.zoom(0, 0.3);
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Come on! Hurry up! You're not getting any
bigger! That would be me!\c[0]
SpriteZoom.zoom(0, 0.2);
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Teensy~ Tiny~! Littler~ and Littler~! I love
making my toys smaller~!\c[0]
SpriteZoom.zoom(0, 0.1);
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Are you going to get here in time? It sure

AlainFace
\n<Alain>It's no use... I can't get anywhere at this
size... Everything's just too huge...
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Ah? Did I do it too much? I think I shrunk
him down to nothing...\c[0]
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Awwww... He was such a fun Itty-Bitty One

While ascending the mountain-sized faerie, Celyn, the
shrunken Alain's size was continuously reduced by his
playful captor.
Though the faerie was already small, every millimeter on
her body grew into meters and then kilometers and then
beyond that with each passing second.
The distance to his goal growing each second, he was
shrunken beyond the point of recognition. His tiny form
was continously reduced to nothing as the body of the
mischievious faerie became his universe.
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Awa?! Hey! Why are you crawling under there?
You won't be able to get to the top with my skirt
covering my undies like that!\c[0]
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Even after all of this, she's still
flustered by me getting close to her
panties? Weren't they the ones saying I
wasn't even worth talking to?
AlainFace2
\n<Alain>That being said... She's right that I
can't climb up. The curve is too much for
me to scale.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Also the air... it's so hot and dense
with a pleasant but heavy scent...
\n<Celyn>\c[27]Mmmghh...! Get away from there already. Don't

\n<Celyn>\c[27]Ehehe~! Did you want to start climbing with

\n<Celyn>\c[27]You're not even bigger than a speck of carpet

\n<Celyn>\c[27]Well, as promised, I'll talk to you~!\c[0]
